#                                                                                                                                                                                                       

[media]

# ABOUT THE GAME

In the Bermuda Triangle, you and your monkey friends have one mission: swing, throw, and climb your way to fun!

[media]

**Play Your Way:** Multiple game modes offer you and your friends different ways to monkey around, including banana collection and cooperative survival. New modes are coming all the time!

[media]

**Get Some Drip:** Customize your body color, equip face & head cosmetics, and stylize your doo.

[media]

**Ruby Mines:** Explore an endless set of tunnels filled with secrets and strange denizens. You can also unlock exclusive seasonal rewards via the Battle Pass, including Cosmetics, Doos, Boosters, and more!

[media]

**Christmas Update**
- New Xmas Battlepass
- Christmas Ornament Hunt
- New Rudolf Bundle
- Christmas Themed Levels

# ABOUT THE GAME

In the Bermuda Triangle, you and your monkey friends have one mission: swing, throw, and climb your way to fun!

![{"height":400,"type":"video","width":1280}](https://scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.7195-25/499303746_2181339939044468_540727540857874572_n.mp4?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=b20b63&_nc_ohc=AF53xS88ILwQ7kNvwEa66zx&_nc_oc=Adm5z_aPPKngdTcKzKCDcpyh8-JmkXJ8kZ11XKV2gtWNf8v5v5HA-1rDuUKDfjBmSdE&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ht=scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=nXBbwkuot2t7cKmrCpQjDA&oh=00_Afux9d1afrF1VLFC8YwzCBfzx-ypAISkMuGUY9qZSiOJLA&oe=6989DF24)

**Play Your Way:** Multiple game modes offer you and your friends different ways to monkey around, including banana collection and cooperative survival. New modes are coming all the time!

**Get Some Drip:** Customize your body color, equip face & head cosmetics, and stylize your doo.

![{"height":400,"type":"video","width":1280}](https://scontent-fra5-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.7195-25/491821117_1430846481437060_8099142216261706884_n.mp4?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=b20b63&_nc_ohc=qUCR0W05QqMQ7kNvwGbWDU1&_nc_oc=AdnQwsN1YmpPnB6IJdtDwGwoVSq2JlVuzW3F1nRmtUcVAA1CmISg-2JzqMI3iLH_C_o&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ht=scontent-fra5-1.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=nXBbwkuot2t7cKmrCpQjDA&oh=00_Afs6pfqAQpXdsr2GT29N0fAohnTtcVjwh4EbdGjMDMcd0A&oe=6989D44C)

**Ruby Mines:** Explore an endless set of tunnels filled with secrets and strange denizens. You can also unlock exclusive seasonal rewards via the Battle Pass, including Cosmetics, Doos, Boosters, and more!

![{"height":1440,"type":"image","width":2560}](https://scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/499292426_757548860702625_520424425045914625_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ZAJAhsjHZaIQ7kNvwEq1MKI&_nc_oc=AdkBjGAbXSIKojzmtKU5GtrpebhPYyeOuSW7JHn4WuVvEMC_mZ-YIYsA7rnpVtta58I&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-fra3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AfuPRQ-L42Zyys9egZVSV4ggALeIi5pDiQC4n_Y7OgW45w&oe=6989D1B2)
